videos.description: Paige Bueckers heaves a full-court pass to Christyn Williams, who lays in a shot to beat the halftime buzzer vs. Notre Dame.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Bueckers’ deep heave sets up Williams’ buzzer-beater) 2021/12/5 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bueckers' deep heave sets up Williams' buzzer-beater

videos.description: In the final minute of action, Paige Bueckers goes down with an apparent knee injury and would be helped off the court.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Paige Bueckers helped off the court after non-contact injury) 2021/12/5 ESHEET

videos.headline: Paige Bueckers helped off the court after non-contact injury
